As police continue  their search  for Boston Marathon bombing suspect Dzhokar Tsarnaev, the Boston area remains frozen. Businesses and schools have closed their doors. Public transportation has screeched to a halt. Residents have been told to stay inside, away from windows, as the manhunt unfolds around them.  Massachusetts Avenue Bridge, Cambridge Watertown Sqaure North Station Area, Boston Congress Street, Boston Longfellow Bridge, Cambridge Massachusetts Avenue, Cambridge (Zara Kessler is an assistant editor and producer for Bloomberg View.  Follow  her on Twitter.)